channel.title: Getting 603 animations on a 317?
channel.description:
Ok, as we know Battlescape is a 317 with all 603 animations and models. I was just wondering how the hell would i do that? I asked if he was loading it on a 603 cache or something but someone said something different but idk... I'm no longer a programmer.
But i was just wondering how was this possible? You cant just take a 603 model from the CacheExtractor and make some ints that have fail invo/drop model zooms then shit on it...
And try to be as specific as possible if you know how to and willing to tell me. Don't go around expecting me to know fucking EVERYTHING.
